Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是什么音？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Si和Re和Do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了So
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs98\b1\pos(960,750)\bord0}So之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确只有这个键发不出声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊 只靠听就能知道是什么音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对音感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是被奈奈子拿来玩的事 没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去下图书室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 那是你昨天才借来的书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经看完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光看书不看到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书签都还留在第一次放的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得真仔细啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不但电影不看到最后 音乐也不听到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.27,0:03:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到一半的时候基本都能猜到了 知道了不就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你还不如不看了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话不能这么说 也有值得一读的好书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我搞不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从哪搞来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs98\b1\1c&H668488&\3c&H443C34&\bord3\blur2\move(960,219.6,960,-28.4,27,1612)}星空之下的演奏会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs60\b1\1c&H668488&\3c&H443C34&\bord2\blur1\move(960,704.4,960,-80,27,4950)}给鲸鱼座Gliese的传话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星空之下的演奏会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给鲸鱼座Gliese的传话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天文台开演奏会？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是要把钢琴曲朝宇宙发送
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周的每天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文台的所长是光的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢琴家是她父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星预报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好使的外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只能看见月亮诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\1c&H252525&\bord0\move(774,232,774,-100,0,1737)}为明天做准备 深夜回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\1c&H252525&\fad(0,500)\bord0\move(615,331,615,-1,0,1779)}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\1c&H252525&\fad(0,500)\bord0\move(618,556,618,221,0,1779)}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\1c&H252525&\bord0\fad(0,500)\move(447,757,447,429,0,1779)}光
